{"tid":609731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上扮女生藉相約看五月天騙財 青年今認罪候判","createTime":"2018-03-29T09:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T10:23:27.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"623b9c17f7336b65789bb1546dabeecfb095a852","tid":609731,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"網上扮女生藉相約看五月天騙財 青年今認罪候判<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180329/large/1522314646_f23c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180329%2Flarge%2F1522314646_f23c.jpg&h=5ef640e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18歲男青年去年在網上交友程式「Skout」假扮妙齡少女，結識男網友後聲稱相約對方看台灣天團「五月天」在港的演唱會，並會代為購票，惟在取得對方2,600元後即失蹤。「假少女」今在裁判法院承認以欺騙手段取得財產罪，獲准保釋候判。<br />\n<br />\n案情指被告林子軒（18歲）去年5月初偽裝少女，成功結識男事主陳凱軒後，雙方透過WhatsApp聯絡，被告於5月12日要求陳將門票錢匯入他的銀行戶口，陳答允及於翌日匯款，惟被告即失去聯絡。警方接報後通緝被告，被告至本月在街頭巴士站被截查時落網，承認已把金錢花掉於與朋友玩樂中。<br />\n<br />\n被告未有聘用律師親自求情，指：「我&hellip;&hellip;願意賠返錢畀受害者。係咁多。」裁判官指被告行騙方式嚴重，需花大量人力物力才可將被告緝捕歸案，將案押後至5月3日判刑，其間候取感化及社會服務令報告。被告獲准以現金1,000元繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n警方草擬的控罪書顯示，被告報稱是裝修工，但法庭考慮判刑日期時，得悉被告實為廣告安裝員，質問他為何向警方報稱從事裝修，被告解釋「我冇呀，我話係廣告安裝。」"},{"pid":"acfda34ffac39ffa91bd05a2c9b4b0202bc53083","tid":609731,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008bf6c9c738dee93ccc323ddbc19b574b62fb4f","tid":609731,"uid":22553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:52:14.000Z","msg":"睇五月天，唔怪得咁易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391d351c96e38dbe0cba0e1b9fb5198a6ecab68e","tid":609731,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9fe4450a87be57536222eb5583cb71bfd0c5660","tid":609731,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"咩係廣告安裝？"},{"pid":"a006c8f368562dca907ef2b3ec18cae75b8719f6","tid":609731,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9仔"},{"pid":"6ddce6f956231c5866931b778c95cb046c09fc37","tid":609731,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:02:40.000Z","msg":"佢應該諗住學佳佳個招🤣🤣"},{"pid":"04e36fb0f4f88588fc966698c8b3054fcf6fc03c","tid":609731,"uid":53121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:05:27.000Z","msg":"點解呢單野條友咁快比人捉到?<br />\n平時IG網購咁多果D過數走數騙案又唔見班黑警拉到人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cdff40b67f8134b364e9c9f29a1ece0c94d4ee","tid":609731,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"堂堂正正請睇五月天咪冇事囉<br />\n<em></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/195044_975e686def813c1ae93082062faf175d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F195044_975e686def813c1ae93082062faf175d.png&h=f62b25b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d47af1d1d88dcf178fd86107c31ed77d71f7dd2","tid":609731,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962e6cc62a242873596c5b345f32b33de37cf094","tid":609731,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"估灑到警犬真係會做野喎"},{"pid":"21bb346b988bd31efca201313679500303cfaafd","tid":609731,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到警犬真係會做野喎</blockquote>"},{"pid":"01db526e26c0334fc5193558d93a2638a6890194","tid":609731,"uid":92064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04e36fb0f4f